%% Ticket board realtime (Socket.IO namespace `tickets`)
sequenceDiagram
    participant Board as TicketsBoard
    participant Facade as TicketsBoardSocketFacade
    participant NS as TicketsNamespace
    participant Room as Room_clientId
    participant Svc as TicketsService
    participant RT as TicketBoardRealtimeService

    Board->>Facade: connect(auth)
    Facade->>NS: Socket.IO connect /tickets
    Board->>Facade: setClient(clientId)
    Facade->>NS: emit setClient
    NS->>Room: join client:clientId
    NS-->>Facade: setClientSuccess

    Note over Svc: After successful DB change (REST or orchestrator)
    Svc->>RT: emitToClient(clientId, ticketUpsert, dto)
    RT->>Room: ticketUpsert
    Room-->>Facade: ticketUpsert
    Facade-->>Board: NgRx merge list or detail

    Note over Svc,RT: Workspace migration (POST /tickets/:id/migrate): for each id,<br/>ticketRemoved on source room then ticketUpsert on target room
